quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,23,"Min dey, mi tawii sonnaajo no laamii …ìe himo okkaa immorde e kala huunde, no woodami mo kadi jullere [laamu] mawnde"
  27,24,"Mi tawii mo kanko e yim…ìe makko …ìen hi…ìe sujjana naange ngen gaanin Alla; Seytaane no cu…óani…ìe golle ma…ì…ìe …óen o faddii …ìe gaayi Laawol ngol, kam…ìe …ìe feewataa"
  27,25,Ko ha…óata …ìe sujjana Alla On yaltinoowo ko suu…óii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi hiMo Anndi ko suu…óoton e ko fe√±inton
  27,26,"Alla, Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Kanko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin. @Corrected"
  27,27,"O maaki: \"Aray men ndaara si a goongu, maa…óum si laati jeyaa…óo e fenu…ìe …ìen"
  27,28,"Yahidu e nduu talkuru am werlo…óaa ndu ka ma…ì…ìe, refti huccaa …ìe ndaaraa ko hon…óum …ìe ruttata"
  27,29,"[Sonnaajo on] wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, min dey werlaama ka am talkuru teddundu"
  27,30,"Pellet, nduu ko immorde e Sulaymaana, pellet, ko woni e mayru ko: \"Innde Alla Huu…ìu…óo Yurmeende Heerii…óo Yurmeende On"
  27,31,"Wata on townitano lam, aree e am ko jebbilii…ìe"
  27,32,"O wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, wa…ótee lam e feere e …óee fiyaake am, mi laataaki ta∆¥oowo fiyaake haa tawde…óon e am"
  27,33,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Enen ko en jooma doole e jooma hare sa…ótu…óe, fiyaake …óen ko ka maa…óa woni, ndaaru ko hon…óum yamirtaa"
  27,34,"[Debbo on] wi'i: \"Pellet, lam…ìe …ìen si …ìe naatii e saare …ìe bonnay nde, …ìe wa…óa teddu…ìe mayre …ìen hoy…ìe, ko wanonii …ìe gollirta"
  27,35,"Awa min, mi nulay e ma…ì…ìe neldaari, mi ndaara ko hon…óum nulaa…ìe …ìen ruttodata"
